equality transfers a zero limit across the Marcinkiewicz-Zygmund normalizer.
-/
theorem durrett2019_theorem_2_5_12_normalized_sum_tendsto_zero_of_eventuallyEq
    {Ω : Type u} {X Y : ℕ -> Ω -> ℝ} {ω : Ω} {p : ℝ}
    (hp_pos : 0 < p)
